divs: Sighting Details planet Venus was very bright that night in Illinois I was in New York and it was raining so my girlfriend took a picture of it and sent it to me as I looked close at photo I saw what appears to be a large ship ufo I cropped the picture to get a better look and send it back to her but before she saw the cropped photo she saw it in the picture she took.. Then she took more photos but it was gone. no doubt in my mind it is a UFO . Peace. J.
Summary: my girlfriend took a picture of Venus and I saw what appears to be UFO
